title: Ultimate Beat  - Too much to lose.
description:
The story of one online poker site that defrauded its customers for years. 

When caught, nobody is arrested, indicted or convicted and the fraudsters paid back far less than they stole.

"rolls out the interviews and the damning paper trail and lets the chips fall where they may, so to speak" - Nolan Dalla
"I was interested in each segment and it never lost my attention." John Mehaffey
